{"tid":257250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"性侵1歲半繼子致死還炫耀　狼父遭20獄友輪暴","createTime":"2017-05-25T06:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T07:44:31.000Z","uid":50769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d4178805049679360ec79546abe0dafb0cb746","tid":257250,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"巴西有一名武術教練，3年前涉嫌性侵自己才18個月大的繼子致死，遭到當地警方逮捕並入獄服刑。不料他非但沒為自己的犯行懺悔，反而還大肆炫耀，引來獄友們的不爽，決定動用私刑好好教訓他。獄友們「以暴制暴」，輪番痛毆並性侵他，讓他的後門受傷嚴重，褲子還沾滿血跡，要讓他好好記住。<br />\n<br />\n根據《The DAILY SCROLLS》報導，這名武術教練名叫夏維爾(Daryell Dickson Meneses Xavier)，3年前涉嫌對年僅18個月大的繼子虐待致死。當時他向外界供稱，繼子是在玩耍時不慎跌倒，送醫急救後因為傷勢過重而在2天後死亡。當地警方得知後介入調查，卻發現案情並不單純。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查發現，小男童身上有多處傷痕，幾乎都是閉鎖性傷口；更讓警方訝異的是，男童的肛門還有嚴重的撕裂傷。經過法醫驗屍結果出爐，員警認為夏維爾涉嫌虐待繼子致死，立刻將他逮捕並且拘禁。<br />\n<br />\n夏維爾被關之後，不但未見反悔之意，甚至還到處炫耀，獄友們聽到之後非常生氣，決定給他一個教訓。約莫有20名獄友聯合起來，不但圍毆夏維爾，甚至還輪暴他，讓他感受繼子生前的恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n夏維爾全身受創，尤其是肛門受到嚴重的撕裂傷，幾乎是血肉模糊，他所穿的白色短褲，幾乎布滿了血跡和髒汙，事後被送到醫院急救和縫合傷口。另外還有消息指出，夏維爾在經過治療後被送回監獄，又被獄友們輪番施暴和性侵。<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"4c3fdd9a144b32580ef99e698332c2f499861f3e","tid":257250,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/730751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F730751&d=3%2Fyb9fo0OzuLUwrjyftdmm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6577326e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/730751</a>"},{"pid":"f57661d2904cb87558d85ea575c452bf45259724","tid":257250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"單新聞好耐啦"},{"pid":"5af893d612b53feb17242ae75cb8902d8f221316","tid":257250,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:31:40.000Z","msg":"Old news is so"},{"pid":"df3298fe74fdd1380deeb1b5e77d338236b634e4","tid":257250,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/25/143229_87e4d7f2994ea27d41f6b44720cec7bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F25%2F143229_87e4d7f2994ea27d41f6b44720cec7bb.jpg&h=e91808d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/25/143230_c983533d1126bd004b10b802cf7e51fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F25%2F143230_c983533d1126bd004b10b802cf7e51fe.jpg&h=bb983996&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dafd8ad8dfe5afc64cdc220643bcc6cb1aa1fcb4","tid":257250,"uid":28271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"Daryl Dixon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a6c4e36c62bd240846bc486dcd076494a9e4bf","tid":257250,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:40:03.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2663ed1f5542ff5ddc787c81644db93ac056d507","tid":257250,"uid":88366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"條褲屎色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25513a0eb3e5b10cf5a2ec955a32f78ec52fe4fc","tid":257250,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"*---&gt;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🌻</span>"},{"pid":"ec882c6bee55845bf670ed63a696869f02a16f52","tid":257250,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"又回帶做乜撚野呀<br />\n仲以為坐左時光機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4de595c16ad507d95e5bd50ce25ffde939ccfc","tid":257250,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:44:31.000Z","msg":"xavi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}